H. Lynn Harton 
Executive Compensation
As President & Chief Operating Officer at UNITED COMMUNITY BANKS INC, H. Lynn Harton  made $1,844,203 in total compensation.  Of this total $575,000 was received as a salary, $575,625 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $625,007 was awarded as stock and $68,571 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


